00:27:28.910 --> 00:27:31.360
It's a great privilege to be
able to talk to so many people.

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:32.660
Thank you.

00:27:32.660 --> 00:27:34.690 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Questioner: I have two questions.

00:27:34.690 --> 00:27:40.080
One is -- how are the
libel laws in Columbia

00:27:40.080 --> 00:27:42.700
and do they protect
political cartoons?

00:27:42.700 --> 00:27:45.360
