commentators, political journalists.

00:31:51.520 --> 00:31:54.720
So it's a difficult situation.

00:31:54.720 --> 00:32:06.110 position:56%
I think social media has changed all
this relationship, all this world,

00:32:06.110 --> 00:32:10.280
so dramatically that we are still
grasping with the consequences

00:32:10.280 --> 00:32:12.370
of that in terms of the law.

00:32:12.370 --> 00:32:17.320
We don't really know how that
works in this brave new world.

00:32:17.320 --> 00:32:22.420 position:56%
But I'm afraid that's all I can say.

00:32:22.420 --> 00:32:23.720
Thank you.

